  <summary date="2020-11-28T00:24:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Community Immunity During COVID-19 Act of 2020

This bill requires the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) to award grants to governmental health departments to increase rates of recommended immunizations during the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency. The CDC must also develop, in consultation with specified entities, guidance for health care providers on counseling patients about COVID-19 vaccines.</summary>
